st used sections. You have lots of different options with it: <\/p><ul><li>Asset to be video or image <\/li><li>The size of the asset (as per column width - the more columns, the larger the asset will be).<\/li><li>Whether the assets displays on the left or right (so you can alternate them down a page). <\/li><li>Where the text is placed. eg. sticky to the top left so it scrolls as you scroll down, in the middle, etc. <\/li><li>Whether you'd like to include a Klaviyo form (see below). <\/li><li>Remove the spacing from above\/below the section so it sits flush against the ones above\/below it. <\/li><\/ul>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"You can add a link","button_1_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/australian-blue-sapphire-engagement-rings","button_style":"underline"}},"bfb88fb9-73a6-4edf-9b4e-c63d1e3e0c95":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16172468895913__bfb88fb9-73a6-4edf-9b4e-c63d1e3e0c95-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230620_NMJ_45_0801_crop_007b5269-d77d-417c-873d-1e23be39d582.jpg"}}},"block_order":["template--16172468895913__bfb88fb9-73a6-4edf-9b4e-c63d1e3e0c95-image-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":true,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":true,"klaviyo_form_id":"RNzriB","media_position":"right","media_position_mobile":"bottom","media_width":"7","content_position":"topLeftSticky","subheading":"<p>Slide title<\/p>","title":"<p>This is another text with<em> media section<\/em><\/p>","description":"<p>Here is an example of the text with media with an embedded Klaviyo form. You can get the Klaviyo form ID out of the URL bar when you are viewing the form editor (<a href=\"https:\/\/gyazo.com\/ea3990075d49e964dbd449bcd01efc55\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/gyazo.com\/ea3990075d49e964dbd449bcd01efc55\">see here<\/a>). <\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"85103600-75fc-4808-83b8-823bb2dafe47":{"type"